headline: OpenAI CEO Sam Altman Denies Sexual-Abuse Claims Made by Sister
summary: Ann Altman’s lawsuit says the alleged abuse occurred at the family’s home in Missouri when she and Sam Altman were children.

headline: Holiday Slowdown Arrives in December with Some Silver Linings For Buyers
summary: December 2024 saw a 22.0% growth in homes actively for sale compared with the same time last year, according to the December Monthly Housing Trends Report from Realtor.com®. Miami (45.4%), San Diego (42.4%), and Denver (41.9%) led the way with the highest active listing growth year over year amongst the top 50 metros in the U.S.
